interface-name: string
in path

ID of interface-name

interface-name: string
in path

ID of interface-name

nv-satellite-id: string
in path

ID of nv-satellite-id

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

interface-name: string
in path

ID of interface-name

interface-name: string
in path

400 Bad Request

in path

in path

in path
